cessibleMode()` helper. Note that `WithAccessible()` is only available on forms, not individual fields, so wrap confirmations in a form:\\n   582→```go\\n   583→form := huh.NewForm(\\n   584→    huh.NewGroup(\\n   585→        huh.NewConfirm().\\n   586→            Title(\\\"Confirm action?\\\").\\n   587→            Value(&confirmed),\\n   588→    ),\\n   589→)\\n   590→if isAccessibleMode() {\\n   591→    form = form.WithAccessible(true)\\n   592→}\\n   593→if err := form.Run(); err != nil { ... }\\n   594→```\\n   595→\\n   596→### Key Points\\n   597→- Always use the accessibility helpers for any `huh` forms/prompts\\n   598→- Test new interactive features with `ACCESSIBLE=1` to ensure they work\\n   599→- The accessible mode is documented in `--help` output\\n   600→\"}]},\"uuid\":\"edd3af13-bd77-4e5b-8b35-4995446eaa02\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-19T03:15:43.111Z\"},\"normalizedMessages\":[],\"type\":\"agent_progress\",\"prompt\":\"You are scoring a code review issue for PR #403 on entireio/cli.\\n\\nThe PR: \\\"fix: restore sessions\\\" - removes stored transcript paths from checkpoint metadata for location independence. It deletes `ResolveSessionFilePath` and `homeRelativePath` from the strategy package, removes `TranscriptPath` fields from checkpoint metadata structs.\\n\\nThe CLAUDE.md files are at:\\n- /Users/alex/workspace/cli/.worktrees/1/CLAUDE.md\\n\\n**Issue:** CLAUDE.md was not updated despite the PR modifying strategy behavior. CLAUDE.md says under \\\"When Modifying Strategies\\\": \\\"Update this CLAUDE.md when adding or modifying strategies to keep documentation current.\\\" The PR removes exported functions and fields from the strategy package and changes how transcript paths are resolved during restore.\\n\\nRead the CLAUDE.md to verify what it says about updating it, and check whether the CLAUDE.md content is actually stale after this PR's changes.\\n\\nScore this issue on a scale of 0-100:\\n- 0: Not confident at all. This is a false positive th